data.description:
Welcome to this luxurious ranch home newly renovated with all the bells and whistles, including brand-new hardwood floors, stone surfaces, and custom-built cabinetry. The kitchen is a chef’s delight, with waterfall quartzite countertops, a gas range, stainless steel appliances, an 11-foot island, and a pantry with tons of storage! Just off the kitchen, is the dining room that features coffered ceilings, and an oversized sliding glass door to the patio and backyard. The main floor study/office offers built-in cabinets, desk and shelving!

Every bedroom will surprise you with their size and two of the main floor bedrooms share a jack-and-jill bathroom, with dual sinks! The sunroom includes massive storage shelves that go all the way up to the ceiling and two dog rest areas built in! In the basement, you will be surprised by the size of 2100 sq feet where there are two bedrooms, a suite, a kitchen-sized wet bar, and an 11-speaker Dolby Atmos home theater with a 150-inch screen! The home theater includes a raised platform so all moviegoers can be entertained with comfort.

The property itself is 2.79 acres (the largest in the neighborhood), it is fully fenced with vinyl split rail, and has a separate fenced backyard! The backyard includes multiple patios, new landscaping with a large grassed area (with sprinklers), and a gas run for a fireplace addition! The fully fenced-back pasture is perfect for horses.
